Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集的又是些一般的提議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}的格式與紀律相違的提議
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被學園祭實行委員會給剔除了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  還是很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像混起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昨天聖櫻學生會幹事送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  整理的時候似乎不小心混進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲避球大會？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意圖也算清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:35.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「學園對抗賽 躲避球大會  6月15日 決賽」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不參加嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好感動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這些就放在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說可以嘗試著做一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知道你們打算怎麼播放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的機會  封套也一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要也登上聖櫻的網頁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都登上去吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:31.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上去吧  登上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是糖果研究會的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拜託一件事  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  當然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自學生會室翻新以來  已經過了兩周了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.97,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}星期一就太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉球時手不要伸開  應該用身體曲成團抱住球來捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲避的時候  應該向對方的慣用手那一側躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為若向慣用手的外側發力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應速度會更慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量也相對較小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽  真是博識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在問別人之前  好歹自己先在網上搜索一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好我會碰巧  偶然  不時地從這門前路過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偶然路過而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去壘球部幫忙了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼精神呢  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…其實呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒——！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說這樣的話  沒有時間去找代替的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒有辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壘球部的神崎明天無論如何都要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  要另外找個人代替才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先說好了  我可不是那種甚麼事都幫一把的老好人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉的時候  身體要曲成團
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲避的時候  應該向對方的慣用手那一側躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毅力不夠！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到球的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是學園躲避球對抗賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:25.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（拼盡全力  加油吧!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們聖櫻策劃  號召附近的高中參加的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園躲避球對抗大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在能有五所高校響應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於今天在這裡聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  這個…看準對方的慣用手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲避的時候  要看準對方的慣用手那一側
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉的時候  身體曲成團抱住！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣還不夠！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到球的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}學生會會長  角澤多佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好不容易來我們這兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是佈置的了不起的學生會室呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的籌備  感覺做得也很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「隊伍請務必要展現學生會幹事的風采」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「比賽結束之後  我們還準備了聯誼會」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今誰也沒有想過  各個學校之間能建立起一種橫向的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許這樣可以找到  各自擔負著的問題的解決的突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個開端就是對抗賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…也許我只是單純地想  大家友好相處會更快樂些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做炒麵的材料不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  天宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喊學美就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以發郵件聯繫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也要  郵箱地址給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳咳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能在百忙之中聚集各位  真是十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是值得紀念的第一屆學生會幹事聯誼會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  複雜的話就不多說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為大家不先做好朋友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會有甚麼真正的好意見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天大家就吃些好吃的東西  高興地聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣了  如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要那樣的話  躲避球不就已經足夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得聚在了一起  說些有意義的話題會比較好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:12.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  又不是來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺一定要商談一下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不成體統呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想做甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做點甚麼有意義的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意義的話題甚麼的…完全沒有準備啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日的議題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓學園生活變得生機勃勃  令人興奮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做才好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生機勃勃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人興奮？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:43.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是做甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不成體統呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼意思  不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討論一下這個怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論哪個學校  都差不多是要準備這個的時期了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為共同的議題不是正適合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}學園的同學既然這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作決定的可是聖櫻學園的同學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就…就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  結果學美就這麼一言未發地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在角澤多佳子同學的帶領下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是不至於冷場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會幹事聯誼會  就這樣消化不良地結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:11:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也會演變成那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲避球比賽也算是盛況空前了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先對現有的成績感到滿足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  加些調料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一碗炸醬麵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我為你擔心了好半天呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭…嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好像都很困呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們叫醒的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（前方是愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}學園站）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一下這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本就能瞭解愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}的學園祭是怎麼一回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麼不知道的就問我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大部分的問題我都是能答上來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打擾你真是對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼  倒是我這邊該為昨天的事說聲對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有你們自己的做法…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在擔心  是不是被你們討厭了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事  多虧了多佳我們才不至於變得很尷尬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幫了我們大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  蜜柑？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛……吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛……呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們覺得怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於學園祭  你們找到甚麼靈感了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點失去信心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳這裡的學園祭真的很出色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像突然出現了一個難以達成的目標一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼努力都趕不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  不管是學校的水準  還是學生的數量都不是一個檔次的  沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:15:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  既然資料也拿到了  我們就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  給這裡添麻煩就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了  角澤學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我認為角澤學姐是一位非常出色的學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我們也會努力辦一個不輸給…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們是不可能贏的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們也會努力辦一個不輸給愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}的學園祭的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候請一定要來玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們走好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人來的話總覺得有點心虛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  反正我也挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是甚麼值得感謝的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說  角澤學姐最後究竟是想說甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼啊…  光香你一直在想這個啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是想讓我們付咖啡的錢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美是怎麼想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們走好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚飯是豬肉泡菜和四季豆豆莢的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是進入叛逆期了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前…衝！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:44.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（學園祭構思筆記）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（生機勃勃  令人興奮）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學…學美  有甚麼話想對哥哥說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能等明天再說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在電話裡說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就想說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在電話裡說不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校集合——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你到底想幹甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時間把我們叫出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道多佳她想說甚麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想說甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳是想告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實不管甚麼樣的學園祭  我們都能辦起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像多佳的學校那樣出色的學園祭也辦起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的學園祭也是能辦起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的學園祭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是把愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}的學園祭照抄過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用以愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}那樣的學園祭為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是由我們所構思的  只有我們能辦得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界獨一無二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦得到的  因為甚麼事情還都沒有決定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一片空白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  甚麼都辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們來描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一片空白之上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界獨一無二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我們的學園祭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是一個人  而是大家一起——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我們的…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是才被人教訓過說要再認真一點嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  聽了剛剛的那番話  總覺得我們辦得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四話  『廣告推行之卷』
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:17.20,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}一定才剛剛開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:24.01,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}千里之行始於足下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:30.88,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}一開始的時候無論是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:38.42,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}都不可以恐慌  這才是最重要的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:47.70,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}選擇了自己所喜歡的道路真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:54.91,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,600)}神啊  我要因此而感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:23:03.21,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)}如今的Lucky  請好好地珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.43,0:23:06.48,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Happy並持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:10.30,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}來吧  保持著這股勢頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:13.14,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Bang！Bang！Bang！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.31,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是呢  Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:18.90,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如今正是時候  Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:22.03,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}把握住機會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:27.20,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}努力地生活下去吧
